eco-battery (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Slope-aware charge scheduling: charge at the valley, discharge at the
    peak and through the descent; 2-unit deadband for near-flat segments
  * Tray status shows next scheduled behaviour change with absolute time
  * Real country grid demand profiles for all 15 bundled countries
  * Active discharge via charge_behaviour (force-discharge / auto)
  * Default max charge lowered to 95% to reduce time at high SoC
  * Safe exit: force-discharge always cleared on quit or SIGTERM

 -- Petr Salomoun <petr.salomoun@gmail.com>  Wed, 11 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0100

eco-battery (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Renamed project from ecco-battery to eco-battery
  * Fix settings persistence: config directory updated to ~/.config/eco-battery

